			<li><a href="http://eleanorg.org">Nor</a> is my lover. I helped build her <a href="http://php.net/">PHP</a>-based <a href="http://ox4.org/~nor">website/art experiment</a>. She also does <a href="http://radicalx.ox4.org">radicalX</a> sex-positive activist art.</li>
