			<li>My pal <a href="http://ultrabobban.blogspot.com/">Bobban</a> runs ultra marathons for some crazy reason.
			</li>
			<li>Crispin and Fi are pals from a long while back and blog about their <a href="http://www.sy-revolution.com/blog/blog1.php">Mediterranean Yachting adventures</a></li>
			<li>Tom has a site called <a href="http://geecologist.org/">Geecologist</a>, geddit?! He used to be my flatmate back in the day.</li>
			<li><a href="http://www.phillipadsmith.com/">Phillip Smith</a> used to work with me at New Internationalist, he blogs about tech and the interwebs.</li> 
